This sample application and libraries is used for showing how web applications can be created using the erlang programming language 
and the yaws web server .
This application will also demonstrate how to 
create web sockets using yaws,
create tcp servers 
parsing iso8583 messages
when its finally done .
in progress .....


the yapp_test_lib contains libraries for the application . 
the yapp_test is the web application
will demonstrate the below when done .
*session management using yaws
*yaws ehtml features
*templating with erlydtl
*working with mnesia(which is a kv store bundled with erlang)
*working with external databases using sumodb
